          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The prize for each weekly sweepstakes is described on the sweepstakes detail screen at entry time. Prize is non-transferable and has no cash equivalent unless explicitly stated. Winner is responsible for any applicable taxes per Mexican law."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El premio de cada sorteo semanal se describe en la pantalla de detalle del sorteo al momento de entrar. El premio es intransferible y no tiene equivalente en efectivo a menos que se indique explícitamente. El ganador es responsable de cualquier impuesto aplicable conforme a la ley mexicana."
          }
        }
      }
    },
